title: Svetlana Romashina - the artistic swimmer with five Olympic gold medals
description:
Russia's Svetlana Romashina has dominated her sport for over a decade. After Rio 2016, she gave birth to a daughter and is aiming to make a comeback to win more Olympic titles at Tokyo 2020. The five-time Olympic champion talks mentality, winning, and her favourite figure skaters.

Find more episode at www.olympicchannel.com/podcast
